## <a name="pause-resume-stop-remove-or-otherwise-control-a-storyboard-interactively"></a><span data-ttu-id="30793-103">ストーリーボードの一時停止、再開、停止、削除、またはその他の制御</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="30793-103">Pause, Resume, Stop, Remove, or Otherwise Control a Storyboard Interactively</span></span>  
 <span data-ttu-id="30793-104"><xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Storyboard%2A> を対話的に一時停止、再開、削除、または制御できるようにするには、その <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> の <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A> プロパティを設定し、<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ControllableStoryboardAction> オブジェクト (<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PauseStoryboard>、<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ResumeStoryboard>、<xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.StopStoryboard>など) を使用して、その <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A>を参照して制御します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="30793-104">To be able to pause, resume, remove, or otherwise control a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Storyboard%2A> interactively, set the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A> property of its <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> and use a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ControllableStoryboardAction> object (such as <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.PauseStoryboard>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.ResumeStoryboard>, or <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.StopStoryboard>) to control it by referencing its <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="30793-105"><xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> の <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A> が指定されていない場合、開始後に <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Storyboard%2A> を対話的に制御することはできません。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="30793-105">If the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Name%2A> of <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard> is unspecified, the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.BeginStoryboard.Storyboard%2A> cannot be interactively controlled after it is begun.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="30793-106">詳細については、「[方法: イベントトリガーを使用してストーリーボードを制御する](/dotnet/framework/wpf/graphics-mul